The '''Summerside Tour''' was the name for a concert tour by [[Jatz/Legends|jatz]] musician [[Fitz Roi]], sponsored by [[fast food]] chain [[Flangth-2-Go]]. The event was preempted shortly before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]<ref name="GNN4">{{JournalCite|4|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref> after Roi used his antique [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrowers]] to shoot numerous historical artistic artifacts in the [[Teirra Parko]]'s [[Crystal Room]] on [[Rimma]].<ref name="GNN3">{{JournalCite|3|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref>

